{"tid":1404293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣狗出手了!] 聽講公僕要對特首完全忠誠喎??","createTime":"2019-08-04T03:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:40:54.000Z","uid":264065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"294be04848f7e0ab4d8c3cbc831418c107256bdc","tid":1404293,"uid":264065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"政府打壓良心公務員！發聲明阻聯署集會：公僕須對特首完全忠誠<br />\n<br />\n 根據《公務員守則》，公務員必須保持政治中立，不論本身的政治信念為何，<span style=\"color: red;\">公務員必須對在任的行政長官及政府完全忠誠</span>，並須竭盡所能地履行職務，不得受本身的政治信念支配或影響。就任何公務員違規的情況，特區政府會按既定機制嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n覺得對家啲文宣唔掂, 諗住幫手將佢地份聲明出返張圖等大家一目了然!!<br />\n<br />\n誓死追隨特首呀!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFYI: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/01/P2019080100742.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F01%2FP2019080100742.htm&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USKnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=df96ba6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/01/P2019080100742.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整埋字又點話??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29155a5df9c5985cf2972f47b4020ff2447faa3","tid":1404293,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"政府要幾冇自信先需要呢啲虛假嘅效忠？"},{"pid":"7e3361c2f7348d2611aadf23ee6731e15d3813c0","tid":1404293,"uid":152492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"零違和感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas